     At the top of the Skills and Abilities panel you can see the "Skills" section (framed). The first number after the skill's name is its current value, the second number is the price of increasing it by one unit.

     To learn more about each skill, place the cursor over it and read the text which appears in the Descriptions panel.

     To increase a skill click on the corresponding button.
     To confirm or cancel your changes, click on the appropriate buttons in the "Your Experience" section.
